import { downloadTemplateExcel1 } from "@/api/common";//封装的后端接口，用于下载文件
export default {
	data() {
		return {
			uploadFileList: [],
			//1待转化 2转化中 3已完成 4转换成功 5失败
			statusType: {

				return "转换成功";
			} else if (this.statusType.fail === val) {
				return "失败";
			} else {
				return "--";
			}
		},
		deleteRow(index) {
			this.uploadFileList.splice(index, 1);
		},
		beforeUpload() {},
		//获取token
		async uploadFileFun(param) {
			//if (param.file.type === "application/pdf") {
			let targetRecord = {
				recordNo: this.uploadFileList.length + 1,
				name: param.file.name,
				status: 1,
				tip: null,
				param: param
			};
			this.uploadFileList.push(targetRecord);

			// }
		},
		async exchangeFile() {
			let fileQuene = this.uploadFileList.filter(item => item.status === 1);
			let i = 0;
			let ret = [];
			let executing = [];
			let enqueue = () => {
				if (i === fileQuene.length) {
					return Promise.resolve();
				}
				let item = fileQuene[i++];
				let uploadPromise = this.uploadProcess(item.param, item);
				ret.push(uploadPromise);
				// promise执行完毕，从executing数组中删除
				let e = uploadPromise.then(() => executing.splice(executing.indexOf(e), 1));
				// 插入executing，表示正在执行的promise
				executing.push(e);
				let r = Promise.resolve();
				if (executing.length >= 2) {
					r = Promise.race(executing);
				}
				return r.then(() => enqueue());
			};
			return enqueue().then(() => Promise.all(ret));
		},
		uploadProcess(param, targetRecord) {
			return new Promise(resolve => {
				let formData = new FormData();
				formData.append("file", param.file);
				//上传并下载
				targetRecord.status = this.statusType.working;
				echangeExcel(formData, {
					"Content-Type": "multipart/form-data"
				})
					.then(
						res => {
							targetRecord.status = this.statusType.finish;
							if (res.headers.hasOwnProperty("content-disposition")) {
								//上传成功后下载转换文件
								const link = document.createElement("a");
								let blob = new Blob([res.data], { type: "application/vnd.ms-excel" });
								//获取heads中的filename文件名
								let temp = res.headers["content-disposition"].split(";")[1].split("filename=")[1];
								temp = decodeURIComponent(escape(temp));
								link.style.display = "none";
								link.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
								link.setAttribute("download", temp);
								document.body.appendChild(link);
								link.click();
								document.body.removeChild(link);
								targetRecord.status = this.statusType.download;
								resolve();
							}
						},
						async err => {
							if (err.data) {
								let resText = await err.data.text();
								let rspObj = JSON.parse(resText);
								targetRecord.tip = rspObj.message;
								targetRecord.status = this.statusType.fail;
							} else {
								targetRecord.tip = "源文件已被修改";
								targetRecord.status = this.statusType.fail;
							}
						}
					)
					.catch(err => {
						console.log(err);
						//this.$message.error("上传失败");
					});
			});
		},
		handleUpload() {
			// 获取 Upload 组件实例
